data.description: 37 acres with a nice house and 3 acres of pasture that held livestock, horses etc. A giant enclosed garage and storage room/workshop and 2 more storage sheds and a concrete pond about 20 x 30 feet, beautiful westward views and and the Santa Cruz river wash that borders the property.
data.whatILove: We love the views and quiet of this place as well as being 20 minutes away from midtown, plenty of space and flat land with tons of potential as a ranch or horse property.
